name: HicPixels#001
description: Homage to the true OG artists from our history. Those pieces are so recognizable and so amazing, that even breaking it down to 21x21 pixels we can still see it. Squish your eyes to see it better. ;) Art that is almost indestructible. This never cease to impress me. No beauty on this art comes from me. It's a inception of stealing. Warhol painted this picture of Marilyn over a photo of Gene Kornman. He added a twist to it. And I added another one.
